&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic and motivated Band 5 nurse to join the team on the Acute Medical Unit based at Ealing Hospital. This is a fast paced and busy 30 bedded unit that provides acute medical and nursing care for patients admitted with a variety of acute medical conditions. We have a strong emphasis on multi-disciplinary team working and in the delivery of high quality, safe patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a band 5 nurse who is keen to develop their skills, knowledge and experience in acute medical nursing. You will need to work well within the team and display good communication and interpersonal skills. In return we offer excellent training and development opportunities. The unit also benefits from a Practice Development Nurse who can support you in your development.&lt;/p&gt;
